  <body>
    <div xml:id="PN259">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>ēṟuṭaip perunirai peyartarap peyarā</l>
<l>tilaiputai peruṅkāṭṭut talaikaran tirunta</l>
<l>valviṉ maṟava roṭukkaṅ kāṇāy</l>
<l>cellal cellal ciṟakkaniṉ ṉuḷḷa</l>
<l>murukumeyp paṭṭa pulaitti pōlat</l>
<l>tāvupu teṟikku māṉmēṟ</l>
<l>puṭaiyilaṅ koḷvāṭ puṉaikaḻa lōyē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>See the self-control of the bold men with strong bows</l>
<l>who sit hidden in the leaf-covered big wilderness</l>
<l>without moving while the large herd with the bull moves.</l>
<l>Don’t go, don’t go – let your mind be superior,</l>
<l>like a Pulai woman’s who impersonates Murukaṉ,</l>
<l>oh you with anklets, decked with a bright swords shining at the sides –</l>
<l>after the cows that gallopp and leap.  </l>
</lg>
    </div>
